metadata.description:
The team presents their ideas for the focus week to gain support and form teams around the selected projects. The theme of this focus week is “helping the community”, and the chosen projects are noted in the youtube links below.

00:00 Introduction
03:53 Implement Object Behavior Prototype
06:03 Draft Spec for the CMP
08:47 Emitting Telemetry Data
13:58 Reference Frame Transformation Library
18:50 Customizable Interactive Visualizations
20:32 Make the Lego Robot Reproducible
23:34 Extract Habitat Simulator Wrappers -- Chosen
28:09 Test Bed for Compositional Objects -- Chosen
31:36 Bounded Evidence Exponential Moving Average (EMA) Neurons -- Chosen
39:25 Monty Flame Graphs
44:53 Implementing 2D Sensor Module
46:51 Salience Showdown -- Chosen
50:44 Interpretive Neuron Dancing

Get the code: https://github.com/thousandbrainsproject/tbp.monty
